title: 'Boys and Girl - SNF Vikings Loss Reaction; Potential Garrett Replacements; The Athletic Cowboys Writer Jon Machota

description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby recap the brutal week 10 loss to the Vikings. Who might be in consideration for the job if Jason Garrett were fired? Plus, Jon Machota from The Athletic stops by..Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys' community.
